                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing clinker and co-producing rich CO/H2 by catalyzing limestone reductive decomposition through thermal plasma coupled gas reducing agent",
                    "一种热等离子体耦合气体还原剂催化石灰石还原分解制熟料并联产富含CO/H2的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method for preparing clinker and co-producing CO/H2-rich clinker through catalytic reduction decomposition of limestone by coupling thermal plasma with a gas reducing agent, which comprises the following steps of: adopting one or more than two of hydrogen, methane-rich gas and ammonia gas as a reducing agent, and supplying heat by utilizing thermal plasma; and catalyzing the reducing agent and limestone in a reactor to be subjected to one-step reductive decomposition to generate clinker, and simultaneously co-producing CO/H2-rich gas. According to the invention, the generation of carbon dioxide by thermal decomposition of limestone can be avoided, the gas rich in CO/H2 is co-produced, the specific composition of the gas is related to a reducing agent and reaction conditions, and the gas can be used as a main component to be supplied to urban coal gas or used as a synthetic feed gas of high-value chemicals such as olefin, oil products and aromatic hydrocarbon. The device has the electrothermal conversion efficiency gt; and the method has the characteristics of long electrode service life, simple process, high added value of products, low industrialization difficulty, easiness in separation of the products, good process repeatability, safety and reliability in operation and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种热等离子体耦合气体还原剂催化石灰石还原分解制熟料并联产富含CO/H2的方法，采用氢气、富含甲烷气、氨气中的一种或两种以上的混合气作为还原剂，利用热等离子供热，在反应器中催化所述还原剂与石灰石一步还原分解生成熟料，同时联产富含CO/H2的气体。本发明可避免石灰石热分解产生二氧化碳，同时联产富含CO/H2的气体，气体具体组成与还原剂和反应条件相关，可作为主要成分供给城市煤气，或作为烯烃、油品、芳烃等高值化学品的合成原料气。本发明具有电热转化效率>90％、电极寿命长、过程简单、产品附加值高、工业化难度小、产物易于分离、过程重复性好、操作安全可靠等特点。"
                }
            ]
